details.name: Ghostship
details.description: Summons a ghostly ship that sails through the battle before smashing apart, damaging and stunning all enemies caught near the wreckage. Allied heroes touched by the Ghostship are given a swig of The Admiral's Rum, receiving bonus movement speed and a delayed reaction to incoming damage. Upgradeable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Drags enemies with the Ghostship towards the crash site. Enemies are still able to perform actions while being dragged.
